  "Description": {
    "English": "A unique ID <span class=\"name name-technology\">transponder</span>, ripped from the internal signal array of an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">outlaw starship</span>.<br><br>Possesion of such a device implies the destruction of the vessel in question. Turn it over to an envoy of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mercenaries Guild</span> to collect any associated bounties.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从一艘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">亡命之徒飞船</span>的网络信号矩阵中取下的独特ID<span class=\"name name-technology\">应答器</span>。<br><br>拥有这种设备意味着原始飞船已被彻底摧毁。将应答器交给<span class=\"name name-technology\">雇佣兵公会</span>的使者以收集对应赏金。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "具有唯一識別碼的<span class=\"name name-technology\">應答器</span>，取自<span class=\"name name-stellar\">亡命之徒太空船</span>的內部訊號陣列。<br><br>擁有這種裝置表示賊人的太空船損毀。上交應答器給<span class=\"name name-technology\">傭兵公會</span>的使節，即可領取相關賞金。"
  },
